Guide for mobile testing:
 - find ur computer ip address (eg 192.168....) (find ip for mac https://www.wikihow.com/Find-Your-IP-Address-on-a-Mac, on windows just type ipconfig in command promt and on wireless its the IPv4)
 - replace it on variable host (top of main.js in folder resources/static/js)
 - make a hotspot on ur pc and connect ur mobile to it (due to secure uni and halls internet providers)
 - connect through ur mobile to address 192.168....:3000 (ip of pc)